android.car.projection

类 ProjectionOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.car.projection.ProjectionOptions

  • public class ProjectionOptions
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds OEM customization for projection receiver app. It is created by Car Service.

    • 字段概要

      字段 
      限定符和类型 字段和说明
      static int AP_MODE_LOHS_DYNAMIC_CREDENTIALS
      Projection access point was created as local-only hotspot, without Internet access and the credentials will be auto-generated for every access point initialization.
      static int AP_MODE_LOHS_STATIC_CREDENTIALS
      Projection access point was created as local-only hotspot, without Internet access and the credentials will persist reboots.
      static int AP_MODE_NOT_SPECIFIED
      Indicates that head unit didn't specify information about access point mode.
      static int AP_MODE_TETHERED
      Projection access point was created such that it may provide Internet access.
      static int UI_MODE_BLENDED
      Show status and navigation bars.
      static int UI_MODE_FULL_SCREEN
      Immersive full screen mode (all system bars are hidden)

        public static final int AP_MODE_NOT_SPECIFIED

      • AP_MODE_LOHS_STATIC_CREDENTIALS

        public static final int AP_MODE_LOHS_STATIC_CREDENTIALS
        Projection access point was created as local-only hotspot, without Internet access and the credentials will persist reboots. Credentials still can be reseted by user or app request.

    • 方法详细资料

      • getUiMode

        public int getUiMode()
        Returns combination of flags from View.SYSTEM_UI_FLAG_* which will be used by projection receiver app during rendering.

      • getProjectionAccessPointMode

        public int getProjectionAccessPointMode()
        Returns projection access point mode.

        The result could be one of the following values:

        • AP_MODE_NOT_SPECIFIED
        • AP_MODE_TETHERED
        • AP_MODE_LOHS_DYNAMIC_CREDENTIALS
        • AP_MODE_LOHS_STATIC_CREDENTIALS

      • getActivityOptions

        public ActivityOptions getActivityOptions()
        Returns ActivityOptions that needs to be applied when launching projection activity

      • getConsentActivity

        public ComponentName getConsentActivity()
        Returns package/activity name of the consent activity provided by OEM which needs to be shown for all mobile devices unless user accepted the consent.

        If the method returns null then consent dialog should not be shown.

        public Bundle toBundle()
        Converts current object to Bundle
